# Schola

## Overview

Schola (`schola.org.my`) is a Malaysian online career exploration platform targeting students aged 13–19 (Form 1 through SPM leavers). It provides bilingual (English / Bahasa Malaysia) job guides, education pathway information, and salary data anchored to the Malaysian context.

## Core Offerings

- **Job guides** — structured career profiles with salary ranges (RM), education pathways, demand outlook, and expert interview quotes
- **Ola chatbot** — AI assistant surfacing job guide content conversationally (see [[ola]])
- **Social media presence** — Instagram (`schola.my`) and TikTok accounts with career-education content

## Audience

- Primary: Malaysian secondary school students (13–19), Form 1 – SPM leavers
- Language mix: English, Bahasa Malaysia, Manglish

